  <acis:phrase id='not-satisfied-with-automatic-search'>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <p>
          Review your name variations (<a ref='#variations'>below</a>).
            The automatic search
          will only find documents matching these name
        variations.</p>
      </li>
      
       <li><p>Your name may be misspelled in our
       bibliographic data. The automatic search will not
       find papers where your name is misspelled.  Try using
       <a ref='@research/search'>a manual search</a>.
       </p></li>

       <li><p>It is likely that the documents you’d like to have
       listed are not in our database.</p></li>

    </ol>

